            Fixes in Open Object Rexx 4.1.1

The following is the list of bug fixes added to ooRexx since the 4.1.0
release.

All Bugs
=============

 * 3491069  ListChoice Routine Doc discrepancy

 * 3488682  Bug in handling of stems after SysStemInsert & SysStemDelete

 * 3482638  SysFileTree returns too many files for '*.' mask

 * 3471889  Invalid statement in smtp.cls

 * 3468276  SysToUnicode : wrong tests of translateflags

 * 3462502  SysFileCopy missing on Linux rehl55 platform

 * 3447211  IF.testGroup contains errors ? (rev. 7320)

 * 3411663  Socket method recvFrom should set address

 * 3386137  rexxpg.pdf: wrong description in 9.14.26 RexxDirectoryPut

 * 3367256  SysStemInsert into empty stem; stem.0 = 0

 * 3315359  rexxpg.pdf error "REXX_TYPED_METHOD"

 * 3305514  .Package does not have "newFile" class method

 * 3296960  Trace -100 displays tracing

 * 3290909  replaceAt method bug in MutableBuffer

 * 3285359  SysUnLink missing fro docs

 * 3279812  NOBUFFER option ignored for WRITE

 * 3274050  Cannot write file to which I don't have read

 * 3205178  SockGetHostByAddr wont work

 * 3187459  Array section method does not accept an array-style index

 * 3185834  HOSTEMU: a DISKR cause file to be created

 * 3184047  error in sample

 * 3178760  RexxLocalVariables::live - only mark if not NULL

 * 3178574  On *nix Move libraries to /usr/lib

 * 3139337  mimemultipart cannot set attribute type

 * 3139083  use of .context is crashing interpreter

 * 3138013  CSVStream remembers headers inapropriately

 * 3137873  rxapi looping

 * 3131745  make clean deletes ylwrap

 * 3046566  SockGetHostName problems

 * 2982725  The Integer class is not supposed to show through

 * 2970679  Array~sort fails with large array

 * 2916971  Cannot compile grxtreestore on 64-bit ubuntu

 * 2895044  RexxGtk

 * 2863294  i386-apple-darwin9.8.0 does not compile.

 * 2846301  SysStemSort very,very slow ....

 * 2832094  RexxTry using wrong path for Documentation on Linux

 * 2811792  librxsock.so relocation error

 * 2811711  rexximage multiple inclusions

 * 1153642  Stem created / returned by a proc wrong in SysDumpVariables


